DTEND;TZID=America/Toronto:20260707T153000
SUMMARY:Zumbini® for Babies (birth to 12 months)
LOCATION:7755 Bayview Avenue\, Thornhill\, ON L3T 4P1
DESCRIPTION:Zumbini® is for you and your baby. It not only provides a wond
 erful workout for adults\, but it also provides the opportunity for infant
 s to experience the sounds and rhythm of the music and movements. Zumbini
 ® encourages parent-infant bonding while enhancing all areas of developme
 nt. It’s a great way connect with other families and educators.\n\nDrop-
 in\n\nCentre: EarlyON Thornhill Centre\n\nSource: https://www.missioninc.c
 om/cso/york/en-ca/earlyon/calendar
