SUMMARY:Let's Talk (birth to 6 years old)
LOCATION:3990 14th Avenue\, Markham\, ON L3R 0B2
DESCRIPTION:Join us for the opportunity to speak with educators and other f
 amilies. Topics may include child development\, available community inform
 ation\, newcomer and pre- and postnatal supports. Community partners may a
 lso join to offer their expertise.\n\n**Come join York Region Public Healt
 h’s Child and Youth Dental Team for optional free oral screenings for ch
 ildren.** \n\nScreenings are quick visual checks inside the mouth conducte
 d by a dental hygienist\, who can provide individualized education and ref
 errals as needed. Please note that a parent or caregiver must be present f
 or any optional dental screening.\n\nA brief presentation on children’s 
 oral health will also be provided for families.\n\nPre-registration requir
 ed\n\nCentre: EarlyON Markham Centre\n\nSource: https://www.missioninc.com
 /cso/york/en-ca/earlyon/calendar
URL:https://www.missioninc.com/cso/york/en-ca/earlyon/calendar
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
